description:
Canaveral Towers 906 is proudly managed by â€˜Happy Palm Staysâ€™.

This 2-bedroom, 2-bath condo with a direct ocean view offers a stylish retreat that fulfills all your Cape Canaveral vacation desires! Its prime location strikes the perfect balance: situated just a mile north of the pier for beach privacy, yet a short stroll down the shore brings you to the vibrant activities at the Pier and Ron Jon's. With easy access to the white sand.

The space
Youâ€™re steps from the white sand, and an easy drive or bike ride to the bars, restaurants, and shops of Cocoa Beach and Orlando.

An open floor plan combines the living room with a spacious, full kitchen. A master bedroom with a king bed and an ensuite bathroom. The convenience of a washer and dryer in the unit, and two twin beds in the guest bedroom! Located on the quiet shores of Cape Canaveral with views of the Kennedy Space Center, the Banana River, and the Cocoa Beach Pier. You are also close to Port Canaveral, Kennedy Space Center, and Theme Parks. Come relax and enjoy this ocean oasis!

Excellent complex amenities:
- Heated & oceanfront pool that is largest in the area
- 2 shuffleboard courts
- Putting green
- Tennis 1 block away.

Other features of this home include:
- Free Wifi
- Free Parking
- Linens & Towels
- Washer & Dryer
- A king bed, two twin beds, and a queen air mattress
- Fully Equipped modern kitchen
- Beach items included (beach chairs, boogie boards, cooler, beach towels)
- Hair Dryer, Shampoo, Conditioner, Body Wash

BOOKING TIP: Discounts are automatically applied for stays 7 nights & greater! The longer you stay, the bigger the discount!

reviews.comments:
Without a doubt this is one of the best Airbnbs that I have stayed at.  Only a couple blocks (5 min walk) to the beautiful ocean, 20 minutes from the Kennedy Space Center where we saw a rocket launch!!!  Easy drive to Orlando for the theme parks. 

Location was perfect but even better was the perfectly kept villa with the private covered and heated pool.  We had a family of five stay here very comfortably and thoroughly enjoyed our time.  The inside is very modern with all updated items and they provide beach chairs, bodyboards, pool noodles and more.  They customize everything in a cute way with GypseaSol cups, towels and even playing cards.  

I would easily recommend this stay for anyone who is interested in a Florida vacation, you wont regret it
Absolutely wonderful location and breathtaking views. Plan on booking again next year and making annual visits to Cocoa Beach!

What a great place to stay! Itâ€™s right on the beach. Beach area wasnâ€™t too crowded. The pool was nice! The place was clean and had everything you would need for the beach, plus everything in the kitchen you would need. It was very clean. We had a great view of the beach, the port and also saw several launches from the front door! We will definitely be back!
reviews.response: So glad you had a blast! Love that you caught some launches too such a cool bonus! Canâ€™t wait to have you back for more coastal magic.

reviews.comments: The location was perfect! Minutes from the beach, beach was practically a private beach. We loved being able to use the beach chairs, bikes, surfboards, which the kids loved. The house the beautiful and comfortable fit a family of 6. Couldnâ€™t have asked for a better place!
reviews.response: So glad you and the family had an awesome time! Love hearing the kids had a blast too. Hope to welcome you back soon!
